  Localizable.strings
  Scribe — base English catalogue.

  Convention: keys mirror the UI surface they appear on. We use
  semantic keys ("welcome.title") rather than the English text
  itself so the en value can be tweaked for tone without breaking
  every translation downstream.
*/

